SELECT "Sales"."product_id" AS "product_id",SUM("Sales"."quantity") AS "total_quantity" FROM "Sales" LEFT JOIN "Product" ON "Sales"."product_id"="Product"."product_id" GROUP BY "product_id"
SELECT "product_id",SUM("quantity") AS "total_quantity" FROM "sales" GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT "P"."product_id",SUM("S"."quantity") AS "total_quantity" FROM "Product" AS "P" JOIN "Sales" AS "S" ON "P"."product_id"="S"."product_id" GROUP BY "P"."product_id"

SELECT "p"."product_id",COALESCE("tmp"."total_quantity", 0) AS "total_quantity" FROM "Product" AS "p" JOIN (SELECT "product_id",SUM("quantity") AS "total_quantity" FROM "Sales" GROUP BY "product_id") AS "tmp" ON "p"."product_id"="tmp"."product_id"
